## Column glossary

- **Mean Top Score** — average score of the top-ranked result across all queries in the fixture.
- **Matches** — number of queries where the top result was flagged as a match (score ≥ threshold).
- **% Matches** — matches as a percentage of total queries. For true-positives this is recall; for true-negatives this is the false-positive rate.
- **ID Recall** — *(positives only)* percentage of queries where the expected entity appeared anywhere in the top-5 results, regardless of match flag.
- **ID Matched** — *(positives only)* percentage of queries where the expected entity appeared in the top-5 results **and** was flagged as a match.
- **Mean ID Rank** — *(positives only)* average rank of the expected entity across queries where it was found.

